  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a123ce28915346e69124075",
      "text": "デライトのLLM Wiki",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dac3",
      "text": "from [2026/05/22]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dac4",
      "text": "デライトのLLM Wiki",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779636839
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ea50000000000376be3",
      "text": "\t2026/5/25 [みやすいビュー https://nishio.github.io/llm-wiki-about-delite/]([Quartz])をつけた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580582,
      "updated": 1779636965
    },
    {
      "id": "6a12476e0000000000376be5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779582830,
      "updated": 1779582830
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dac5",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580582
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dac6",
      "text": "\t(文脈: [造語の意味の理解]に関しての議論)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ea70000000000376be4",
      "text": "\trawの中の特定文字列の出現箇所を見てその文字列の意味を推定しconceptsに書く、というサイクルをLLM Wikiにさせればよいのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580583,
      "updated": 1779580583
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dac7",
      "text": "\t\t既存の概念と簡単に対応するなら簡単に解説され、そうでないなら長文で解説される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dac8",
      "text": "\tというわけでデライト関連文書をClaude Codeが読んでまとめるLLM Wikiを作った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dac9",
      "text": "\t\tまだ見やすいビューはつけてない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7daca",
      "text": "\t\t[輪郭 https://nishio.github.io/llm-wiki-about-delite/wiki/concepts/utagawa/%E8%BC%AA%E9%83%AD]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779636876
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dacb",
      "text": "\t\t\t[ユージン・ジェンドリン]ぽさがあるな〜と思ってたが、そもそも主要概念の多くが[ジェンドリン https://nishio.github.io/llm-wiki-about-delite/wiki/people/ジェンドリン]のそれと一致するし、思想的にはWhiteheadを親とする兄弟みたいなものなのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779636896
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dacc",
      "text": " \t\t\t>宇田川氏自身が「17歳以降に傾倒した哲学者」として Whitehead と David Bohm を挙げている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dacd",
      "text": "    > [Whitehead] の[プロセス哲学]（『[Process and Reality]』1929）は、ジェンドリンの 'A Process Model' の理論的祖。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dace",
      "text": "    > ジェンドリンはホワイトヘッドを継承しつつ、身体・暗黙・言語の関係 を独自に展開した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a12449400000000004bb540",
      "text": "   おもしろい[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1779582100,
      "updated": 1779582108
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dacf",
      "text": "\t　[最終的に4つのまとめ記事が作成された https://nishio.github.io/llm-wiki-about-delite/wiki/syntheses/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779636917
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dad1",
      "text": "\t\t　おもしろい[caki.icon][taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779585926
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dad2",
      "text": "\t\t　井戸端ユーザーそれぞれ毎にこういうwiki作ると面白そう[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dad3",
      "text": " デライトの輪郭がsourceになってる！面白い[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779580131,
      "updated": 1779580280
    },
    {
      "id": "6a123ce20000000000b7dad4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
